   00 | ------ IMark(0x4000be, 2, 1) ------
   01 | t0 = GET:I32(itstate)
   02 | t1 = Shr32(t0,0x08)
   03 | t231 = GET:I32(cc_op)
   04 | t232 = GET:I32(cc_dep1)
   05 | t233 = GET:I32(cc_dep2)
   06 | t234 = GET:I32(cc_ndep)
   07 | ------ IMark(0x4000c0, 2, 1) ------
   08 | t7 = Shr32(t1,0x08)
   09 | t243 = And32(t1,0x000000f0)
   10 | t242 = Xor32(t243,0x000000e0)
   11 | t241 = Or32(t231,t242)
   12 | t847 = armg_calculate_condition(t241,t232,t233,t234):Ity_I32
   13 | t250 = CmpNE32(t243,0x00000000)
   14 | t848 = ITE(t250,t847,0x00000001)
   15 | t253 = And32(t1,0x00000001)
   16 | t252 = Xor32(t253,0x00000001)
